CSSLAB - sandbox project for css frameworks
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

This project exists as a playground for trying out and evaluating different css frameworks.
Ease of use, clear path for extensions and possibility to create responsive web designs (one site suitable for smart phone, tablet and desktop) are important parameters.

Evaluated frameworks are (each in their own subdirectory):
* Bootstrap - https://github.com/twitter/bootstrap
* Foundation - https://github.com/zurb/foundation
